  "id": "piston-door-2x2",
  "title": "2x2 Piston Door",
  "category": "door",
  "description": "A compact 2x2 sliding door. Four sticky pistons surround a 2-wide, 2-tall gap: two below the gap face UP and two above it face DOWN. When powered they all extend and their heads fill the four opening blocks (closed); cut the power and the sticky heads retract, clearing the gap (open). One lever drives all four through a redstone line that climbs the back of the wall, so a single flip opens and closes the whole door.",
  "aliases": ["2x2 door", "piston door", "hidden door", "redstone door"],
  "inputs": ["lever"],
  "outputs": [],
